{
  "texts": [
    "These gene sets contain many sets that are made of orphan GPCRs and Znf family members.",
    "Other sets are mainly modules of differentially expressed genes.",
    "These modules are likely serving critical biological roles but are less explored.",
    "Next, we noticed that the Rummagene collection of gene sets has many duplicate entries.",
    "In fact, duplicated gene sets make up approximately 15% of the Rummagene gene sets."
  ]
}